statement.p:
Suppose that $\ltdefn{T}{U}{V}$ is a linear transformation and

S&=\set{\vectorlist{u}{t}}

spans $U$.  Then

R&=\set{\lt{T}{\vect{u}_1},\,\lt{T}{\vect{u}_2},\,\lt{T}{\vect{u}_3},\,\ldots,\,\lt{T}{\vect{u}_t}}

spans $\rng{T}$.

